title: Kiss: Man, Man, Medium-Light Skin Tone, Dark Skin Tone
description: Depicts two men kissing, with specified medium-light and dark skin tones. Represents romantic love and affection between two men.
apple_vendor_description: This emoji, as rendered on Apple devices, showcases two men in a loving embrace, with one man displaying a medium-light skin tone and the other a rich dark skin tone. Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and realistic lighting give the figures a distinct depth and warmth. The tender expression and close proximity communicate deep affection, partnership, and romantic connection, beautifully represented on Apple devices.
